(1128, 576, 'Informed him about the total cost in New Zealand. He currently have around 10 lacs in savings and will take an education loan for the rest. Will connect him with the loan dept.', 'Follow Up', 'Discussion', 6, '2025-10-14 23:19:31', '2025-10-14 23:19:31'),
(1129, 576, 'According to NZ POC, the following conditions must be fulfilled:\r\n- Last 3 years ITR - 10 lacs+\r\n- Funds must be maintained for at least 6 months\r\n- Only collateral loan can be taken\r\n- Loan disbursement and then maturing the funds is mandatory\r\n- IELTS - 6.5 not less than 6\r\n- Legit gap justification', 'Follow Up', 'Discussion', 6, '2025-10-14 23:22:47', '2025-10-14 23:22:47'),
(1130, 576, 'Informed his father about the same and suggested him to change the country as his son is not eligible for NZ. He said he\'ll get back to us.', 'Follow Up', 'Discussion', 6, '2025-10-14 23:24:57', '2025-10-14 23:24:57'),
